frames.caption: A young woman sits contemplatively on the edge of a narrow, water-filled alleyway. The scene is set against a backdrop of dilapidated buildings under a dramatic, cloud-filled sky. Her expression is introspective as she gazes at the water below.
frames.description: The scene depicts a solitary moment in an urban setting, with a focus on the woman's introspective mood. The environment appears worn and abandoned, suggesting themes of solitude and reflection.

frames.caption: A young person sits on the edge of a rain-soaked street, surrounded by crumbling buildings. The sky is overcast with dark clouds, suggesting a recent or ongoing storm. The individual appears contemplative, with their head bowed and hands resting on their knees.
frames.description: The scene depicts a solitary figure in an urban environment, likely after a rainstorm. The setting is characterized by dilapidated buildings and a reflective puddle on the ground, creating a somber and introspective atmosphere.
